OL,4,CRussian food firm VkusVill triggers row
OL,5,Cover lesbian family ad
OL,6, Russian health food chain VkusVill has
OL,7, triggered a storm of criticism on
OL,8, social media for posting an online
OL,9, advertisement showing a lesbian family,
OL,10, then removing it and apologising.
OL,12,FThere was anger from those for and
OL,13,Fagainst the ad, which ran on VkusVill's
OL,14,Fwebsite under the slogan "Recipes for
OL,15,Ffamily happiness".
OL,17,FThe firm said the ad was intended for
OL,18,Fpeople aged 18 and above.
OL,20,FRussia bans any content deemed to be
OL,21,Fspreading gay "propaganda" to minors.
